text:
This question is for Andre Nguyen specifically, what UI implementation/features are you most proud of?
Techy boring answer: I worked with our lead programmer Kevin to create a system where I can tell objects to animate from any part of the screen to another, even with different aspect ratios and points that change position. This is most obvious when you evade a monster, or when you use a healing spell/ability.
Silly answer (but also just as true): TENTACLES!
